r />\n竟然係香港。。"},{"pid":"681c6767c5672be45a0575fa7792562ff8657df1","tid":845995,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"行西隧快d咪行西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都唔得"},{"pid":"e77b14ab5ec1300c8b40e0abd48ad4d9b90a84da","tid":845995,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"8629aad75a6a002f99672ae6e83bb1783796d072","tid":845995,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"香港城管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817fa6d0fc63f21a2d64b13a1bea135a66d1a665","tid":845995,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"庭上播放現場的閉路電視片段，可見馬押解司機至接近警車門口時，司機將身體放軟。林姓警員登上警車，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用右手箍住司機頸部並向上扯</span>，馬則捉著司機雙腳。司機上車後表現仍然不合作，更下車躺在警車門對開路面。<br />\n<br />\n咁整法咩都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過個的士佬又係既，無啦啦打人仲拒捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a585cea24d8a96619f252b27fe8f16678432a3","tid":845995,"uid":181703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"警察又會話係合法武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43faa5ce1bc760a282a3ddd3559d4cc8d94e2cdd","tid":845995,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家 得自己一個重病"}]}